text: International Communist Party (in Spanish: Partido Comunista Internacional) is a small communist group in the Dominican Republic. The president of the party is Wilson del Obre. The party has an office in connection with del Obre's family residence on the Engombe highway, Herrera, Santo Domingo. ==References== *Listin Diario *Diario Libre Category:Communist parties in the Dominican Republic Category:Political parties in the Dominican Republic
